not quite like this.

BIC:  All of a sudden a canaster of the mutant virus falls and infects 
a protoform in the middle of the room.  It then comes on line and 
copies Protohuman and Eagle dna.  It also copies small amounts of 
Necromancer's and Veratis's dna although not enough to effect it's 
appearance plenty to give it new powers.  An angle suddenly flies from 
the pod and out the base before anyone can stop it.  Anyone got a 
problem with that?
